Classes in be.kuleuven.micas.signalStorage.interfaces used by be.kuleuven.micas.signalStorage
IndexedSignals

          ReloadableSimulationOutput is an interface that indicates that a SimulationOutput can be loaded.
NamesIndex
          SimulationOutputHeader provides a view on the names and units that exist in a simulation output file.
SignalDatabase
          SimulationOutput stores raw simulation output data, these are waveforms (signals) which can be accessed by their name or by their index.
